"title": "5833: diligence",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5833: diligence",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Conscientious hard work and perseverance, particularly with regard to a relationship with God. In Scripture diligence is highly commended. It may, however, be misguided.</p>\n<h2>Diligence and its results are commended</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov21:5\">PRO 21:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs11:28\">1KI 11:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr24:13\">2CH 24:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra5:8\">EZR 5:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra6:12\">EZR 6:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra7:23\">EZR 7:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov12:14\">PRO 12:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov14:23\">PRO 14:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov31:17\">PRO 31:17</a> <em>characteristic of the wife of noble character</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl3:13\">ECC 3:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:16\">JER 31:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor8:11\">2CO 8:11</a> <em>regarding the collection for the poor Christians in Jerusalem</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim5:17\">1TI 5:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:2\">1PE 5:2</a></p>\n<h2>Diligence contrasted with laziness</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:4\">PRO 10:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov12:24\">PRO 12:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov12:27\">PRO 12:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov13:4\">PRO 13:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess3:10\">2TH 3:10</a></p>\n<h2>Diligence is important in the outworking of one's relationship with God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:58\">1CO 15:58</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim4:15-1Tim4:16\">1TI 4:15–4:16</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Examples of diligence</h3>\n<p><em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr15:15\">2CH 15:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr29:34\">2CH 29:34</a> <em>the Levites</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa62:6-Isa62:7\">ISA 62:6–62:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech6:15\">ZEC 6:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:15\">LUK 8:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:11\">ACT 17:11</a> <em>the Bereans</em><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:15\">ROM 1:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor4:12\">1CO 4:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor9:24-1Cor9:26\">1CO 9:24–9:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor6:5\">2CO 6:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor11:27\">2CO 11:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess2:9\">1TH 2:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess3:8\">2TH 3:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:7\">2TI 4:7</a>\n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:8\">ROM 12:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom16:12\">ROM 16:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:31\">1CO 12:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor14:1\">1CO 14:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor8:5\">2CO 8:5</a> <em>the Macedonian churches</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:12-Phil2:13\">PHP 2:12–2:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:12\">1TH 5:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb6:11-Heb6:12\">HEB 6:11–6:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:10\">2PE 1:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:2-Rev2:3\">REV 2:2–2:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:19\">REV 2:19</a></p>\n<h2>Diligence was a characteristic of Jesus Christ's mission</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:51\">LUK 9:51</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:1-Heb12:2\">HEB 12:1–12:2</a></p>\n<h2>Misguided diligence</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:39-John5:40\">JHN 5:39–5:40</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps127:2\">PSA 127:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov28:20\">PRO 28:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl1:3\">ECC 1:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl2:11\">ECC 2:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl2:19\">ECC 2:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl4:8\">ECC 4:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:15\">MAT 21:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:23-Matt21:24\">MAT 21:23–21:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:10\">1TI 6:10</a></p>",
